<text><body>
<lb ed="F" n="0118a16"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><juan fun="open" n="1"><jhead>大王觀世音經一卷</jhead></juan>
<lb ed="F" n="0118a17"/><div1><p id="pF01p0118a1701"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">佛</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;</rdg></app>說觀世音<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">經一卷</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">讀誦</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>千遍得度苦難拔除生死罪觀世音菩薩南&CB07099;佛佛國有緣佛法相因
<lb ed="F" n="0118a18"/><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">常樂</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>我<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">淨</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;</rdg></app>　&unrec;&unrec;<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">南&CB07099;摩訶波若</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>是大神&CB00057;　南&CB07099;摩訶波若是大明&CB00057;　南&CB07099;摩訶波若是大
<lb ed="F" n="0118a19"/>&unrec;等等&CB00057;　<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">淨光祕密佛</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>　<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">法藏</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>佛　師子吼神足遊王佛　告須&CB07460;登王佛　法護佛　金剛
<lb ed="F" n="0118a20"/><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">藏師</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>子游戲佛　藥師&CB00222;璃<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">光</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;</rdg></app>佛　普光功德山王佛　善住功德寶王佛　六方六佛名&CB00561;　東
<lb ed="F" n="0118a21"/>方寶光月<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">殿</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;</rdg></app>妙尊音王佛　南方樹根華王佛　西方<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">皂</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;</rdg></app>王神通<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">焰</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&CB00672;</rdg></app>華王佛　北方月殿清淨佛
<lb ed="F" n="0118a22"/>　上方&CB07099;數精進寶首佛　下方善寂月音王佛　釋迦牟&CB00112;佛　&CB07460;勒佛　中央一切眾生在此
<lb ed="F" n="0118a23"/><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">世</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;</rdg></app>界中者行住於地上及<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">在虛空中慈憂</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>於一切令各安休息晝夜脩治心常應誦此經消伏於</p></div1>
